cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.NE 

The paper deals with a computer vision problem of remote heart rate estimation from face videos. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of deep neural networks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.LG (Machine Learning), or both. Additionally, the paper discusses the limited annotated samples, which could indicate that it belongs to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
